[30;1m5945 | [0m[35m        frame-change errors and branching them outward in tandem, until one of them wins[0m

[30;1m358 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m359 | [0m[35m            Pauli feedback operations don't need to be performed on the quantum[0m
[30;1m360 | [0m[35m            computer. They can be performed within the classical control system.[0m
[30;1m361 | [0m[35m            As such, it often makes sense to skip them when sampling from the[0m
[30;1m362 | [0m[35m            circuit on hardware, and then account for this later during data[0m
[30;1m363 | [0m[35m            analysis. Turning on this flag means that the quantum computer[0m

[30;1m71 | [0m[35m*   **Bottom up.**[0m
[30;1m72 | [0m[35m    Stim is intended to be like an assembly language: a mostly straightforward layer upon which more[0m
[30;1m73 | [0m[35m    can be built.[0m
[30;1m74 | [0m[35m    The user may define QEC constructions at some high level, perhaps as a set of stabilizers or as [0m
[30;1m75 | [0m[35m    matrix, but these concepts are explained to Stim at a low level (e.g., as circuits).[0m
[30;1m76 | [0m[35m    Stim is not necessarily the abstraction that the user wants, but Stim wants to implement low-lev[0m
[30;1m77 | [0m[35m    pieces simple enough and fast enough that the high-level pieces that the user wants can be built[0m

[30;1m120 | [0m[35m    When doing general stabilizer simulation, Stim tracks the inverse of the stabilizer tableau that[0m
[30;1m121 | [0m[35m    used.[0m
[30;1m122 | [0m[35m    This has the unexpected benefit of making measurements that commute with the current stabilizers[0m
[30;1m123 | [0m[35m    linear time instead of quadratic time. This is beneficial in error correcting codes, because the[0m
[30;1m124 | [0m[35m    they perform are usually redundant and so commute with the current stabilizers.[0m

[30;1m35 | [0m[35m[0m

[30;1m37 | [0m[35m            P at the start of the circuit to the instantaneous stabilizer Q at the end of[0m
[30;1m38 | [0m[35m            the circuit. The flow may be mediated by certain measurements. For example,[0m
[30;1m39 | [0m[35m            a lattice surgery CNOT involves an MXX measurement and an MZZ measurement, and[0m
[30;1m40 | [0m[35m            the CNOT flows implemented by the circuit involve these measurements.[0m
